          "confidence": "medium",
          "horizon": "months"
        },
        {
          "ticker": "UMC",
          "rationale": "UMC is the most direct Taiwanese competitor to Hua Hong on mature 28nm/40nm/55nm specialty nodes (power management, display drivers, MCUs). Hua Hong capacity constraint is a near-pure-play tailwind for UMC pricing and share.",
          "confidence": "high",
          "horizon": "months"
        },
        {
          "ticker": "GFS",
          "rationale": "GlobalFoundries competes directly with Hua Hong on mature/specialty nodes for automotive, IoT, and RF. US-based, no China exposure risk, benefits from customers seeking non-Chinese mature-node supply.",
